data.description: WELCOME TO 621 OBRIANS PATH! This lovely home is gorgeously appointed and is much larger than it looks from the outside. Step into the 2-story foyer with a separate living room and dining room to your right and left. The spacious family room is open to the oversized gourmet kitchen just waiting for its aspiring chef! There's also a breakfast nook with a screened patio leading to the private backyard. The owners suite is also on the main but tucked away so you still have your privacy. Head upstairs where you'll find 4 additional bedrooms, two of which have their own ensuite. That's right, 5 bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms! This home is so inviting and waiting for it's next owner to make it home again.
